snippet.title: Nicole Zara
snippet.description:
"Because the universe needs more lesbians"

Catch-all channel for all women-loving-women content on Shortland Street, despite the specific channel name. Currently that means the main focus is Nicole Miller and Maeve Mullens.  And Leanne and Rosalyn. OMG how are we getting so much content?

A timeline:
Meredith/Annie 1994
Caroline/Laura 1999 
Laura/Madeleine 2000
Maia/Jay 2004-2007
Maia/Nicole 2010-2011, 2012
Maia/Jennifer 2011
Nicole/Lana 2012
Nicole/Bonnie 2013
Nicole/Harper 2014
*Nicole/Ruby 2017
Harper/Dani/(Drew) 2018
*Nicole/Zara 2019
*Nicole/Maeve 2020-
*Saskia/Jodie 2020
*Theo/Hannah 2020-2021
*Leanne/Rosalyn 2021-

*Asterisked pairings are uploaded to this channel

Don't bother asking me to upload whole episodes.

If you're in New Zealand you're probably geoblocked from seeing 85% of the earlier uploads on here sorry, though it's been better recently.
